#: ../../../release_details/9.4/add-graphics-backend-preference-for-webgpu-rendering.md:1
msgid "Add Graphics Backend Preference Option For WebGPU Render Window"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/add-graphics-backend-preference-for-webgpu-rendering.md:3
msgid ""
"`vtkWebGPURenderWindow` now provides a way to choose a graphics backend at "
"runtime. The available backends vary on different operating systems. Here "
"are the available backends:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/add-graphics-backend-preference-for-webgpu-rendering.md:6
msgid "D3D11"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/add-graphics-backend-preference-for-webgpu-rendering.md:7
msgid "D3D12"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/add-graphics-backend-preference-for-webgpu-rendering.md:8
msgid "OpenGL"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/add-graphics-backend-preference-for-webgpu-rendering.md:9
msgid "OpenGL ES"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/add-graphics-backend-preference-for-webgpu-rendering.md:10
msgid "Metal"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/add-graphics-backend-preference-for-webgpu-rendering.md:11
msgid "Vulkan"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/add-graphics-backend-preference-for-webgpu-rendering.md:13
msgid ""
"VTK pre-initializes the render window with a suitable default backend. They "
"are:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/add-graphics-backend-preference-for-webgpu-rendering.md:15
msgid "D3D12 on Windows"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/add-graphics-backend-preference-for-webgpu-rendering.md:16
msgid "Metal on macOS"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/add-graphics-backend-preference-for-webgpu-rendering.md:17
msgid "Vulkan everywhere else"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/add-graphics-backend-preference-for-webgpu-rendering.md:19
msgid ""
"In case a backend is unavailable, the webgpu implementation (Dawn) may "
"fallback to a suitable default or fail to return an adapter."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/add-graphics-backend-preference-for-webgpu-rendering.md:22
msgid "You may indicate preference like so:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/add-graphics-backend-preference-for-webgpu-rendering.md:23
msgid ""
"vtkNew<vtkRenderWindow> renWin\n"
"// requests webgpu implementation for a D3D12 backend\n"
"renderWindow->SetBackendTypeToD3D12();\n"
"// Similarly,\n"
"// renderWindow->SetBackendTypeToD3D11();\n"
"// renderWindow->SetBackendTypeToOpenGL();\n"
"// renderWindow->SetBackendTypeToOpenGLES();\n"
"// renderWindow->SetBackendTypeToMetal();\n"
"// renderWindow->SetBackendTypeToVulkan();\n"
"//..\n"
"renderWindow->Render();\n"
msgstr ""
